ygData.messageBody:
Hail and Well Met Ainthara
Good point about the men LOL. I play on Cazic Thule.
Have a 55 cleric Syphra, 26 warrior Bandalara, 21
ranger Izzabel, 2 wizard Blon. I have played a little
over a year now. Having a blast met alot of
interesting people. Am the guild leader of Valor &
Light. Recently have been leveling the Ranger she's
fun. Have most of my epic items for cleric just need
to spawn Ragefire. Have a great week
Syph
